<div class="container wow fadeInUp titulo">
  <div class="row justify-content-center">
    <div class="col-xs-12">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h1 class="section-title">About us</h1>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="container">
  <div class="row">
      <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-12">
        <% if notice %>
          <p class="notice"><%= notice %></p>
        <% end %>
        <% if alert %>
          <p class="alert"><%= alert %></p>
        <% end %>  
      </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row wow fadeInUp">
    <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-12">
      <img src="<%= image_path("gameslaves.png") %>" />
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row wow fadeInUp">
    <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-12">
      <p>We are a group of six Costa Rican computer engineers trying to make one and the best game develop company of Costa Rica.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row wow fadeInUp">
    <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-12">
      <p>We have a diverse group compound of a 3D artist and modeller, a 2D artist, a writer, two level designers and a awesome programmer.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row wow fadeInUp">
    <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-12">
      <p>Our team have what it takes to make indie games and we hope to develop many of them in the future.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>